task.summary: Default task
Changed old Input usages to new Input System. Added basic game objects to scene.
Fixed GameObject unloading attempt error.
Finished GameObjectMVC factory. Minor refactoring in ScriptableObjectManager.
Removed empty folder.
Renamed main scene. Removed unused code.
Added PrefabPath provider.
Moved PathProvider logic to Core submodule.
Fixed TaskScheduler ignores DelayTask delay.
Fixed PrefabsPaths loading.
Removed unused installer, added PathHandler path initialization.
Added auto path finding for MVC prefabs.
Replaced WorldBuilder with action. Added layer between scene running and Zenject initialization.
Added TaskFactory and WaitForNextFrame yield instruction;
Added GameStateMachine. Moved PlayerLoading to LoadingTask game state.
Added meta file.
Removed obsolete TaskScheduler, replaced with System.Threading.Tasks.Task usages for async code. Added Async instantiation to GameObjectMVCFactory.
Added TaskExtensions to run tasks from synchronous code.
Changed using obsolete TaskScheduler to async/await behaviour for tasks. Added world loading task. Minor namespaces refactoring.
Added OnComplete and OnAbort methods to TaskExtensions.
Added switch to Game state after completing Loading state.
Moved Task events subscription and calling to AsyncTask.
Fixed Tasks execution before it runs through try/catch block in TasksExtensions. Minor refactoring.
Replaced Resources loading to Addressables loading for MVC factory. Covered Editor using in ScriptableObjectsPathHandler with UNITY_EDITOR define. Minor refactoring.
Replaced Resources usages to Addressables. Imported Addressables pack.
Fixed IInitializable Initialize() not being called when an instance created via factory.
Added ModelLoader interface for scriptable objects.
Added PlayerSettings scriptable object. Refactored event naming for Input system. Added walls to the world prefab.
Replaced UnityCallbacksBehaviour with Zenject ITickable system.
Replaced IUnityCallbackBehaviour with Zenject ITickable system.
Minor name refactoring.
Added First Person camera system. Added Cinemachine to the project.
Replaced Cinematic with Camera usage. Added character movement processing.
Moved camera to a separate GameObject.
Added OnLateTick implementation.
Added jump and gravity functionallity.
Minor movement and jump systems fixes and refactoring.
Removed TODO.
Updated Unity version. Changed gravity value for better jump and gravity experience.
Added camera pitch clamp.
Added Playground prefab to test movements and physics.
Added sliding from steep slopes functionality. A bit of playground fixes.
Added sprint functionality.
Added crouch functionality. Added small obstacles to the Playground.
Added character movement animations
Added TextMestPro to the project, added cheats panel. Separated the project for assembly definitions.
Added assembly definition. Extended GameObjectMVCFactory.
Added CheatsPanel loading.
Minor fixes. Added EmptyModel.
Fixed errors.
